metadata.name: Lily
metadata.description:
1/1
Orange lily folds inwards.
Seeking restoration and renewal of her soul.
Releasing the past.

2nd artwork of a series of 7 from the Revival Collection.

A collection of cathartic paintings created to inspire hope for the future.
Journey of the female psyche.

Curated with theme contributions by packphour.

Oil paintings on paper reinvented with digital paintwork for the screen for our
combined visions of the collection.

Oil painting on paper & digital painting.
3000 x 2888 pix
350 dpi

Limited Edition of 10 - Eve
1st artwork in the series
Available to collect on Manifold
http://app.manifold.xyz/c/revivaleve
